## 10. Backend API Base URL for demo JS

The demo JS should call:
```js
const API = 'https://api.michaelwegter.com';
// POST ${API}/art-store/login
// GET  ${API}/art-store/prints
// POST ${API}/art-store/checkout
```

For local dev, allow override:
```js
const API = window.ART_STORE_API || 'https://api.michaelwegter.com';
```
